{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 13''' is the 13th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events ==
* {{ill|Zongzhang (era)|ja|総章|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 / {{ill|Munmu of Silla|ja|文武王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8 ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|668|ja|668th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Tang dynasty|ja|唐|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Silla|ja|新羅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} forces conquer {{ill|Goguryeo|ja|高句麗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , unifying the {{ill|Korean Peninsula|ja|朝鮮半島|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Tenshō (era)|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 15 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1587|ja|1587th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|1=Toyotomi Hideyoshi|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} moves from {{ill|Osaka Castle|ja|大坂城|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Jurakudai|ja|聚楽第|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in Kyoto.
* {{ill|Keichō (era)|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Ishigakibaru|ja|石垣原の戦い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} takes place.
* Keichō 14 (Gregorian {{ill|1609|ja|1609th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Maeda Toshinaga|ja|前田利長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} enters {{ill|Takaoka Castle|ja|高岡城|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , founding the city of {{ill|Takaoka, Toyama|ja|Takaoka City|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in present-day {{ill|Toyama Prefecture|ja|富山県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Births ==
* {{ill|Kyōhō (era)|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 18 (Gregorian {{ill|1733|ja|1733rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Sugita Genpaku|ja|杉田玄白|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a {{ill|Rangaku|ja|蘭方|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} physician (+ {{ill|1817|ja|1817th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
