'''September 13''' is the 13th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . 


== Events ==

* {{ill|Zongzhang (era)|ja|総章|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  1 / {{ill|Munmu of Silla|ja|文武王|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  8 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|668|ja|668th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Tang dynasty|ja|唐|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  and {{ill|Silla|ja|新羅|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  forces conquer {{ill|Goguryeo|ja|高句麗|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , unifying the {{ill|Korean Peninsula|ja|朝鮮半島|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .

* {{ill|Tenshō (era)|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  15 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1587|ja|1587th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|1=Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  moves from {{ill|Osaka Castle|ja|大坂城|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  to {{ill|Jurakudai|ja|聚楽第|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  in Kyoto.

* {{ill|Keichō (era)|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Ishigakibaru|ja|石垣原の戦い|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  takes place.

* Keichō 14 (Gregorian {{ill|1609|ja|1609th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Maeda Toshinaga|ja|前田利長|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  enters {{ill|Takaoka Castle|ja|高岡城|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , founding the city of {{ill|Takaoka, Toyama|ja|Takaoka City|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  in present-day {{ill|Toyama Prefecture|ja|富山県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .

== Births ==

* {{ill|Kyōhō (era)|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  18 (Gregorian {{ill|1733|ja|1733rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Sugita Genpaku|ja|杉田玄白|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a {{ill|Rangaku|ja|蘭方|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  physician (+ {{ill|1817|ja|1817th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==

* {{ill|Keichō (era)|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  5 (Julian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Yoshihiro Muneyuki|ja|吉弘統幸|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|samurai|ja|武将|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  (* {{ill|1564|ja|1564th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).

== Commemorations ==

* {{ill|Jūsan'ya|ja|十三夜|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  (Thirteenth Night)


